OL,3,CPrisons minister: Legislation to ban
OL,4,Cmost short sentences due 'imminently'
OL,6,FITV News Social Affairs Correspondent
OL,7,FSarah Corker sat down with Lord
OL,8,FTimpson. Words by Senior Politics
OL,9,FProducer Lili Donlon-Mansbridge
OL,11,FThe prisons minister has told ITV News
OL,12,Fthat short sentences are a "disaster"
OL,13,Ffor female prisoners, and that his
OL,14,Fgovernment's reforms to women's
OL,15,Fjustice will be "radical".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
