OL,3,CPrisons minister: Legislation to ban
OL,4,Cmost short sentences due 'imminently'
OL,6,FLord Timpson confirmed the government
OL,7,Fwill introduce legislation to ban
OL,8,Fshort sentences, apart from in
OL,9,Fspecific circumstances. When asked
OL,10,Fwhen the legislation would enter the
OL,11,FHouse of Commons, the prisons minister
OL,12,Fsaid it was coming "imminently".
OL,14,F"What's been really clear in the David
OL,15,FGauke review into sentencing is the
OL,16,Fmajority of the recommendations there,
OL,17,FI think, are absolutely the right
OL,18,Fthing. So we've obviously got to go
OL,19,Fthrough the legislation process," he
OL,20,Ftold ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
