OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F308A1751375570
OL,3,CPrisons minister: Legislation to ban
OL,4,Cmost short sentences due 'imminently'
OL,6,F"What is really clear is that we need
OL,7,Fto make sure that we resolve the
OL,8,Fprison crisis, but we also make sure
OL,9,Fthat people can be punished
OL,10,Feffectively outside of prison," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FThe Independent Sentencing Review,
OL,14,Fchaired by Former Justice Secretary
OL,15,FDavid Gauke, recommend the number of
OL,16,Fcriminals being given short prison
OL,17,Fsentences be reduced, in favour of
OL,18,Fcommunity-based punishments, including
OL,19,Felectronic tagging.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
