OL,3,CPrisons minister: Legislation to ban
OL,4,Cmost short sentences due 'imminently'
OL,6,FLord Timpson told ITV News that in
OL,7,Flots of cases short sentences are a
OL,8,F"disaster", particularly for female
OL,9,Foffenders. Last year, the Justice
OL,10,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood outlined the
OL,11,Fgovernment's plans for women's
OL,12,Fjustice, including setting an ultimate
OL,13,Fambition of closing a women's prison
OL,14,Fentirely.
OL,16,F"For a lot of women, being in prison
OL,17,Fon short sentences is a disaster.
OL,18,FTheir children are taken into care and
OL,19,Fthey lose their house, their job.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
