OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F308A1751375570
OL,3,CPrisons minister: Legislation to ban
OL,4,Cmost short sentences due 'imminently'
OL,6,F"My mum was a foster carer and lots of
OL,7,Fthe children who came to live with us,
OL,8,Fespecially babies, they came to us
OL,9,Fbecause their mums were in prison.
OL,11,F"And then when their mums came out of
OL,12,Fprison, they often came to our house
OL,13,Ffor day business and stuff.
OL,15,F"And what was really clear, even from
OL,16,Fwhen I was a teenager, that a lot of
OL,17,Fthese women are very ill. And I still
OL,18,Fbelieve that a lot of the women who
OL,19,Fare in prison are very ill.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
