OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F308A1751375570
OL,3,CPrisons minister: Legislation to ban
OL,4,Cmost short sentences due 'imminently'
OL,6,F"There are some pregnant women that
OL,7,Fcommit really serious offences and
OL,8,Fthat is what prison is for for them.
OL,9,FBut there are also a large number of
OL,10,Fwomen, pregnant women, women with
OL,11,Fyoung children who I believe would be
OL,12,Fbetter off being diverted away from
OL,13,Fprison and serve their punishment in
OL,14,Fthe community", he told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
