OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F308A1751375570
OL,3,CPrisons minister: Legislation to ban
OL,4,Cmost short sentences due 'imminently'
OL,6,F"But also that we divert women away
OL,7,Ffrom prison, but we wrap around
OL,8,Fsupport on housing, mental health and
OL,9,Fdrugs - and that's where the intensive
OL,10,Fsupervision courts, which I'm a big
OL,11,Ffan of, I think they have a big role
OL,12,Fto play too."
OL,14,F"There are far too many people
OL,15,Freoffending and especially women going
OL,16,Fround and round the cycle of
OL,17,Freoffending and creating more
OL,18,Fvictims," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
