OL,6,FHe also acknowledged that the
OL,7,Fprobation service was stretched, but
OL,8,Fsaid that had been given additional
OL,9,Fresource, including in the Spending
OL,10,FReview in March.
OL,12,F"Probation is under a lot of pressure
OL,13,Fand that is where the heavy lifting of
OL,14,Fthe justice system is done, and that
OL,15,Fis where our focus needs to turn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
