OL,3,CPrisons minister: Legislation to ban
OL,4,Cmost short sentences due 'imminently'
OL,6,F"Because for far too long, probation
OL,7,Fhas been the forgotten about service
OL,8,Fin the justice system. And for me, it
OL,9,Fis absolutely vital. That's why we've
OL,10,Fgot 700 million of extra funding.
OL,11,FWe're recruiting thousands of more
OL,12,Fprobation staff," Timpson insisted.
OL,14,FThe prisons minister also reiterated
OL,15,Fthe government's commitment to change
OL,16,Fthe law to stop prisons being used as
OL,17,F'place of safety' under the Mental
OL,18,FHealth Act.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
