OL,3,CPrisons minister: Legislation to ban
OL,4,Cmost short sentences due 'imminently'
OL,6,F"In the Mental Health Act that is
OL,7,Fgoing through Parliament at the
OL,8,Fmoment, that's one of the clear
OL,9,Fobjectives. Prison is not the place
OL,10,Ffor people who are very seriously
OL,11,Fmentally ill. It is in a secure
OL,12,Fhospital environment."
